ldn=E2=80=99t tell you, because I am certainly not in the business of telli=
ng you how to get away with crimes.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But another question you might have is: Does s=
hadow trading=C2=A0<em>happen a lot?=C2=A0</em>Are there a ton of corporate=
 insiders and deal advisers who are regularly making shadow trades in order=
 to profit from inside information? Some casual empirical data:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
